# Hakimi Codex

A modern AI coding assistant CLI tool, inspired by [Aider](https://github.com/paul-gauthier/aider), [OpenAI Codex CLI](https://github.com/openai/codex), and [Kimi CLI](https://www.kimi.com).

---

## Features

- **Clean TUI Interface** - Textual-based terminal UI, no emojis, professional styling
- **Dual Panel Layout** - Left: AI chat interaction, Right: code/diff view
- **Diff Visualization** - Red/green line highlighting for code changes (like Continue extension)
- **Thinking Fold** - AI reasoning content collapsed by default, expandable with 2-line preview
- **Command System** - `/` prefix commands: `/help`, `/setting`, `/model`, `/diff`, `/run`, etc.
- **8 AI Tools** - Command execution, file read/write, directory listing, search, code sandbox, project analysis, web search
- **Multi-Model** - OpenAI, Claude, DeepSeek, Gemini, Mistral, Ollama, custom APIs
- **Settings Management** - Stream output, thinking mode, temperature, font size, colors, themes

---

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install -e .

# Launch
hakimi

# Or specify project directory
hakimi /path/to/project
```

---

## Layout

```
+----------------------------+------------------------+
|  AI Interaction (55%)      |  Code/Diff (45%)       |
|  - User messages            |  - Current file view   |
|  - AI responses             |  - Red/green diff      |
|  - Thinking (collapsible)  |                        |
|  - Tool results            |                        |
+----------------------------+------------------------+
|  > Input (/help, /setting...)                         |
+-------------------------------------------------------+
```

---

## Commands

| Command | Description | Example |
|---------|-------------|---------|
| `/help` | Show all commands | `/help` |
| `/setting` | Show/update settings | `/setting temperature=0.5` |
| `/model` | Model management | `/model list`, `/model select gpt-4o` |
| `/file` | Add file to context | `/file src/main.py` |
| `/diff` | Show file diff | `/diff` |
| `/clear` | Clear chat history | `/clear` |
| `/run` | Execute shell command | `/run python -m pytest` |
| `/status` | Show project status | `/status` |
| `/commit` | Git commit changes | `/commit "fix: bug"` |
| `/exit` | Quit application | `/exit` |

---

## Settings

| Setting | Type | Default | Description |
|---------|------|---------|-------------|
| `stream` | bool | `true` | Stream output |
| `think_mode` | bool | `true` | Show thinking content |
| `think_fold` | bool | `true` | Collapse thinking by default |
| `think_lines` | int | `2` | Lines shown when folded |
| `temperature` | float | `0.7` | AI temperature |
| `font_size` | int | `12` | UI font size |
| `theme` | str | `dark` | UI theme |
| `show_tool_results` | bool | `true` | Show tool execution results |
| `auto_analyze` | bool | `true` | Auto analyze project on start |

Usage: `/setting key=value`

---

## Supported Models

| Model | Provider | Context |
|-------|----------|---------|
| GPT-4o | OpenAI | 128K |
| Claude 3.5 Sonnet | Anthropic | 200K |
| DeepSeek Chat | DeepSeek | 64K |
| Gemini 1.5 Pro | Google | 1M |
| Mistral Large | Mistral | 32K |
| Llama 3 (Ollama) | Local | 8K |

