## Project Structure

```
hakimi_codex/
├── codex/
│   ├── core/          # Core modules
│   │   ├── models.py       # Model definitions
│   │   ├── config.py       # Config persistence
│   │   ├── llm_client.py   # LLM API client
│   │   ├── tools.py        # Tool execution engine (8 tools)
│   │   ├── code_sandbox.py # Python sandbox
│   │   ├── project_analyzer.py  # Project auto-detection
│   │   ├── settings_manager.py  # Settings management
│   │   └── command_handler.py   # Command processor
│   ├── widgets/       # UI widgets
│   │   ├── chat_panel.py      # Chat with thinking fold
│   │   ├── diff_panel.py      # Red/green diff view
│   │   ├── code_view.py       # Code viewer
│   │   ├── file_tree.py       # File tree
│   │   ├── model_selector.py  # Model management
│   │   └── terminal_panel.py  # Terminal panel
│   ├── screens/       # Screens
│   │   ├── main_screen.py     # Main dual-panel layout
│   │   ├── splash_screen.py   # Launch screen
│   │   └── model_edit_dialog.py  # Model editor
│   ├── styles/
│   │   └── codex.tcss    # Theme styles
│   ├── app.py         # Main app
│   └── __main__.py    # CLI entry
├── hakimi.bat         # Windows launcher
├── hakimi.sh          # Linux/macOS launcher
├── requirements.txt
├── setup.py
└── README.md
```

